WEBVTT

01:26.750 --> 01:34.990
[LIVE UP TO YOUR YOUTH]

01:35.539 --> 01:37.979
[Episode 29]

01:38.700 --> 01:41.110
[Joyful]

01:40.150 --> 01:40.880
Shengli,

01:41.190 --> 01:42.210
are you

01:42.229 --> 01:44.200
still selling leather shoes and jackets?

01:44.200 --> 01:44.840
Leather shoes and jackets.

01:44.840 --> 01:45.979
Business is pretty stable now,

01:45.979 --> 01:46.750
so I let the factory

01:46.750 --> 01:47.880
handle it directly.

01:47.880 --> 01:49.080
We found a storefront

01:49.310 --> 01:50.180
on Yabao Road.

01:50.450 --> 01:51.120
We're thinking of

01:51.120 --> 01:52.560
selling some other things

01:52.560 --> 01:55.550
to expand the business.

01:55.690 --> 01:57.100
Scale up the business.

01:57.900 --> 01:59.190
I gotta say, Shengli

01:59.220 --> 02:00.780
is a man of great vision.

02:01.350 --> 02:01.950
How so?

02:01.990 --> 02:03.180
You see,

02:03.700 --> 02:06.200
people usually don't want to change

02:06.260 --> 02:07.790
when they are comfortable.

02:07.990 --> 02:09.250
They usually only do it

02:09.360 --> 02:10.370
when they hit a wall

02:10.370 --> 02:11.430
and have no choice.

02:11.820 --> 02:13.120
But someone like Shengli,

02:13.120 --> 02:14.310
he's always prepared for a rainy day.

02:14.310 --> 02:15.840
His business is doing well,

02:15.920 --> 02:17.360
yet he chose to adapt.

02:17.630 --> 02:18.829
He is extraordinary.

02:19.900 --> 02:21.350
Yeah,

02:21.690 --> 02:23.210
extraordinarily annoying.

02:23.210 --> 02:24.140
Listen to me.

02:25.810 --> 02:28.430
It's all thanks to my wife.

02:31.770 --> 02:33.930
It's all because of my wife.

02:33.950 --> 02:34.460
Come on.

02:34.460 --> 02:35.250
Keep talking like this.

02:35.250 --> 02:36.150
If you speak any louder,

02:36.150 --> 02:37.010
she'll hear us.

02:44.290 --> 02:52.630
[Joyful]

02:46.310 --> 02:47.500
- Thank you, everyone.
- Thank you.

02:47.500 --> 02:48.579
Thank you.

02:49.630 --> 02:50.890
Thank you! Same to you!

02:55.530 --> 02:56.930
Thanks, you too!

02:57.780 --> 02:58.790
Here they come.

02:59.020 --> 02:59.750
We're counting on you, Xiaobao.

02:59.750 --> 03:00.320
Okay.

03:01.400 --> 03:02.330
Happy wedding!

03:02.400 --> 03:03.530
- Thank you.
- We're here.

03:03.530 --> 03:05.900
- Come on.
- Right.

03:07.060 --> 03:08.410
Should I call her Ranran today,

03:08.410 --> 03:09.710
or wifey?

03:09.710 --> 03:10.750
Call her whatever you want.

03:10.750 --> 03:11.610
Call her wifey.

03:12.080 --> 03:12.750
Anything is fine.

03:12.750 --> 03:13.940
Anything.

03:16.630 --> 03:17.250
Wifey,

03:17.250 --> 03:19.150
I'm here to take you home!

03:20.190 --> 03:21.120
Who is it?

03:22.590 --> 03:23.079
Xiaobao.

03:23.079 --> 03:23.579
Xiaobao.

03:23.579 --> 03:24.680
I'm your brother-in-law.

03:24.680 --> 03:26.480
Brother-in-law, open the door!

03:27.210 --> 03:28.550
It's the groom.

03:29.030 --> 03:30.990
Listen up, Groom, hear me well,

03:31.060 --> 03:32.910
Say your hellos, or you’ll stay in your shell.

03:32.910 --> 03:34.940
If the red packets are way too light,

03:34.970 --> 03:37.430
The bride won't be leaving with you tonight!

03:37.800 --> 03:39.800
- Xiaobao, that is a good one.
- Yeah.

03:40.440 --> 03:42.210
Look at this kid.

03:42.400 --> 03:43.810
Are the red envelopes ready?

03:43.810 --> 03:45.740
Brother-in-law, here are the red envelopes.

03:45.740 --> 03:47.950
Here you go.

03:49.180 --> 03:49.980
Pick it up.

03:50.079 --> 03:50.940
Is that enough?

03:52.579 --> 03:54.000
This isn't even enough to share.

03:54.000 --> 03:55.300
Is that all?

03:55.410 --> 03:56.760
You're not sincere.

03:57.810 --> 03:58.410
Come on.

03:58.500 --> 03:59.460
Here's more.

03:59.460 --> 04:00.310
Give them a little at a time.

04:00.310 --> 04:01.850
- A little at a time.
- Okay.

04:02.150 --> 04:03.150
Here's more!

04:03.150 --> 04:03.980
There aren't many people left.

04:03.980 --> 04:04.960
All right, open the door.

04:04.960 --> 04:06.020
Bring them all here.

04:06.020 --> 04:07.810
This won't do.

04:07.870 --> 04:10.890
- Not enough.
- You have to pass Xiaobao's test first.

04:11.020 --> 04:12.020
Okay, no problem.

04:12.190 --> 04:13.830
Xiaobao, test them well.

04:14.190 --> 04:14.580
Okay.

04:14.720 --> 04:15.780
What test?

04:16.050 --> 04:17.149
You sing a song

04:17.180 --> 04:18.980
that Zhuang Zhuang used to sing.

04:19.200 --> 04:20.040
You gotta sing it.

04:20.040 --> 04:21.680
Sing? Sing what?

04:22.600 --> 04:23.520
Hear this one,

04:25.630 --> 04:28.300
I love Beijing Tian'anmen, Bei...

04:28.510 --> 04:29.930
Didn't you sing that?

04:30.000 --> 04:30.650
Yes.

04:30.950 --> 04:31.680
Ranran sang it.

04:31.680 --> 04:32.630
This is Ranran's song.

04:32.630 --> 04:34.130
- Zhuang Zhuang! - Zhuang Zhuang!

04:34.130 --> 04:36.420
- I'm a bit nervous. - [Ocean, My Hometown] is fine too.

04:36.420 --> 04:38.060
[Beat the Hand Drum and Sing].

04:38.060 --> 04:38.720
This works.

04:38.720 --> 04:40.330
The sea...

04:40.330 --> 04:41.310
No, beat the hand drum...

04:41.310 --> 04:43.470
Beat the hand drum and sing a song.

04:46.000 --> 04:48.340
Beat the hand drum and sing a song.

04:48.480 --> 04:49.750
Every

04:49.950 --> 04:51.390
bullet

04:51.450 --> 04:53.140
eliminates an enemy.

04:53.220 --> 04:55.210
We are all flying troops.

04:55.300 --> 04:57.900
Even if the mountains are high and waters deep.

05:12.270 --> 05:14.580
Beat the hand drum and sing a song.

05:14.620 --> 05:18.190
Riding a horse over the hillside.

05:18.510 --> 05:19.810
Open the door.

05:20.510 --> 05:21.920
How was the singing?

05:22.240 --> 05:24.030
You mixed up the songs.

05:24.390 --> 05:25.040
Xiaobao,

05:25.040 --> 05:26.840
let's say they passed this test.

05:27.180 --> 05:28.610
In such a hurry?

05:28.640 --> 05:29.260
Okay.

05:29.540 --> 05:30.640
Next question.

05:30.690 --> 05:33.060
What's the name of the movie brother Xu wrote?

05:33.060 --> 05:34.460
You can't get this wrong.

05:35.270 --> 05:36.590
[The Late Love].

05:36.960 --> 05:37.850
Ranran,

05:38.100 --> 05:38.680
well,

05:38.700 --> 05:40.560
my love for you will never be late.

05:41.010 --> 05:41.890
Open the door quickly.

05:41.890 --> 05:43.240
If you don't open the door,

05:43.240 --> 05:44.000
I'll...

05:44.000 --> 05:45.320
we'll be late. Hurry!

05:46.220 --> 05:47.620
Look how anxious you are.

05:48.510 --> 05:50.180
Are there any other performances?

05:50.180 --> 05:50.710
Yes.

05:50.740 --> 05:52.370
If there's another one, your dad will do it.

05:52.370 --> 05:53.060
Hurry up.

05:53.320 --> 05:54.659
Tell Xiaobao to open the door.

05:54.659 --> 05:55.409
What should I say?

05:55.409 --> 05:56.180
You perform.

05:56.240 --> 05:58.300
- Your son listens to you. Hurry up.
- Your son listens to you.

05:58.300 --> 05:59.430
Listens to me?

05:59.690 --> 06:00.640
Well,

06:00.930 --> 06:02.110
well, Xiaobao,

06:02.980 --> 06:04.840
as a member of the bride's family,

06:04.890 --> 06:07.350
you have to guard this door.

06:09.130 --> 06:10.330
Let me say something.

06:10.430 --> 06:12.160
Ranran calls me uncle.

06:12.310 --> 06:13.300
I'm her elder.

06:13.360 --> 06:14.850
You should bow to me.

06:17.600 --> 06:18.660
Why don't you bow?

06:18.820 --> 06:19.720
Bow.

06:19.750 --> 06:20.940
Brother-in-law!

06:21.220 --> 06:23.010
Look, I'm your brother-in-law.

06:23.010 --> 06:24.010
We'll get along well in the future.

06:24.010 --> 06:25.130
Open the door first.

06:25.130 --> 06:26.190
I still have

06:26.220 --> 06:27.360
a thick stack of red envelopes here.

06:27.360 --> 06:28.330
I can't stuff them under the door.

06:28.330 --> 06:29.160
Leave a crack for me.

06:29.160 --> 06:30.310
Right, just a crack.

06:30.870 --> 06:32.170
Will he play tricks?

06:33.270 --> 06:34.270
Just open a crack.

06:34.560 --> 06:35.140
Okay.

06:35.500 --> 06:36.680
You're in such a hurry to see him.

06:36.680 --> 06:38.190
Don't play tricks if I open a crack.

06:38.190 --> 06:40.050
- I won't.
- I'll just stuff the red envelopes in.

06:40.050 --> 06:41.000
You can't do anything funny.

06:41.000 --> 06:43.060
Come on. Where are the red envelopes?

06:46.220 --> 06:47.280
Xiaobao!

06:50.370 --> 06:52.070
Dear friends,

06:52.240 --> 06:52.800
next,

06:52.830 --> 06:54.680
let's give a warm round of applause

06:54.680 --> 06:56.830
and invite our groom to give a speech.

06:56.860 --> 06:59.800
Great!

07:01.330 --> 07:03.100
Honey, you look beautiful today.

07:03.100 --> 07:04.980
Great!

07:03.210 --> 07:05.980
♪ If I want to look far away ♪

07:05.330 --> 07:06.210
That's it?

07:06.370 --> 07:07.300
Just one sentence?

07:07.300 --> 07:08.430
You're too beautiful.

07:07.930 --> 07:11.020
♪ A cloud can't block the sun ♪

07:10.080 --> 07:11.360
Bride, are you satisfied?

07:11.360 --> 07:12.120
Satisfied.

07:12.450 --> 07:13.710
Let's go then.

07:13.740 --> 07:14.850
The auspicious time has come.

07:14.850 --> 07:18.820
♪ Go to the vast sea with wind and waves ♪

07:14.980 --> 07:16.170
Let's go.

07:16.300 --> 07:17.710
Find the shoes.

07:17.750 --> 07:19.270
The shoes.

07:19.360 --> 07:20.870
The shoes.

07:20.120 --> 07:23.510
♪ Instead of struggling in the pond ♪

07:21.620 --> 07:22.590
Over here.

07:22.620 --> 07:23.430
Let me put them on you.

07:23.430 --> 07:24.780
She took them out herself.

07:24.620 --> 07:27.920
♪ If I have faith in spring ♪

07:26.890 --> 07:28.280
Ranran can't wait.

07:29.450 --> 07:30.970
The bride's feet can't touch the ground.

07:29.450 --> 07:32.690
♪ A rainstorm can't bring away
the fragrance of flowers ♪

07:31.000 --> 07:31.830
We should...

07:31.860 --> 07:33.190
It's the rule of Seasons Change Hostel.

07:33.190 --> 07:33.560
Okay.

07:33.659 --> 07:34.680
You have to carry her.

07:34.680 --> 07:35.190
Okay.

07:35.220 --> 07:36.070
Right?

07:36.120 --> 07:37.460
Yes.

07:36.590 --> 07:40.310
♪ Those dreams that are hard to realize ♪

07:41.390 --> 07:44.620
♪ Have taken root deep in my heart ♪

07:45.050 --> 07:49.510
♪ After countless times of blooming
and withering, I still plant hope ♪

07:51.190 --> 07:55.100
[Seasons Change Hostel]

07:51.830 --> 07:56.030
♪ Seasons change during this trip ♪

07:57.050 --> 08:01.510
♪ My eyes become the stars above ♪

08:02.220 --> 08:04.340
♪ Time goes by bit by bit ♪

08:04.800 --> 08:06.740
♪ Leading you and me ♪

08:07.130 --> 08:10.830
♪ Let days grow into annual rings ♪

08:10.570 --> 08:11.830
Where are you going?

08:11.500 --> 08:15.350
♪ Dreams will witness sunset and sunrise ♪

08:11.960 --> 08:12.860
Aren't you tired?

08:12.860 --> 08:14.320
Put her down here. Come on.

08:16.010 --> 08:20.710
♪ I came to the bustling city ♪

08:16.120 --> 08:16.860
Today

08:16.920 --> 08:20.140
is a happy event for Dongquchunlai.

08:20.310 --> 08:22.070
We need to take a picture, right?

08:21.290 --> 08:23.360
♪ The world is boiling ♪

08:22.160 --> 08:23.690
Come on, photographer get ready.

08:23.690 --> 08:24.420
Listen to him.

08:23.850 --> 08:26.390
♪ Just because someone burned out their youth ♪

08:24.450 --> 08:25.660
Photographer, come here.

08:25.660 --> 08:26.210
Okay.

08:26.240 --> 08:26.820
Come on, everyone.

08:26.820 --> 08:28.520
Everyone, come on, look here.

08:28.220 --> 08:30.410
♪ That's us ♪

08:28.980 --> 08:30.840
We wish Liangliang and Ranran

08:30.980 --> 08:31.890
a happy marriage.

08:31.890 --> 08:32.289
Okay.

08:31.980 --> 08:35.370
♪ If I have faith in spring ♪

08:32.320 --> 08:33.390
Okay, come on.

08:33.880 --> 08:36.330
Three, two, one.

08:36.510 --> 08:41.960
Happy marriage to Liangliang and Ranran!

08:36.900 --> 08:39.770
♪ A rainstorm can't bring away
the fragrance of flowers ♪

08:44.070 --> 08:47.740
♪ Those dreams that are hard to realize ♪

08:48.900 --> 08:52.020
♪ Have taken root deep in my heart ♪

08:52.490 --> 08:56.830
♪ After countless times of blooming
and withering, I still plant hope ♪

08:59.330 --> 09:03.590
♪ Seasons change during this trip ♪

09:04.400 --> 09:09.070
♪ My eyes become the stars above ♪

09:09.570 --> 09:11.570
♪ Time goes by bit by bit ♪

09:12.040 --> 09:13.860
♪ Leading you and me ♪

09:14.450 --> 09:18.040
♪ Let days grow into annual rings ♪

09:18.850 --> 09:22.600
♪ Dreams will witness sunset and sunrise ♪

09:19.720 --> 09:20.840
Coming.

09:23.290 --> 09:27.990
♪ I came to the bustling city ♪

09:24.010 --> 09:25.080
They're coming.

09:28.650 --> 09:30.450
♪ The world is boiling ♪

09:31.040 --> 09:33.560
♪ Just because someone burned out their youth ♪

09:31.530 --> 09:32.300
Mom, Dad,

09:32.320 --> 09:33.520
I'm getting married.

09:35.790 --> 09:36.700
Brat.

09:39.970 --> 09:41.440
[Suyuan Chun Fresh Corn Juice]

09:40.820 --> 09:42.080
Uncle Zhang, Uncle Li.

09:43.240 --> 09:44.440
Let me introduce you.

09:44.440 --> 09:45.200
My mom and dad.

09:45.200 --> 09:46.770
Congratulations.

09:46.350 --> 09:50.530
[Suyuan Chun Fresh Corn Juice]

09:49.050 --> 09:50.330
This is the

09:50.410 --> 09:52.070
Suyuan Chun corn juice I made.

09:52.290 --> 09:54.200
I brought it today for you to taste.

09:54.200 --> 09:55.550
I will send two truckloads of drinks over to your shop.

09:55.550 --> 09:56.270
Thanks.

09:56.790 --> 09:57.920
Congratulations.

09:58.010 --> 09:59.050
No need for this.

09:59.100 --> 10:00.050
Okay, put it here.

10:00.050 --> 10:01.110
Where is the bride?

10:02.030 --> 10:03.090
Where is the bride?

10:04.030 --> 10:05.700
The bride is here.

10:11.860 --> 10:15.610
♪ Light up a brighter life ♪

10:15.630 --> 10:19.660
♪ Spring lingers on ♪

10:15.960 --> 10:16.590
Dad.

10:18.460 --> 10:19.080
Mom.

10:21.050 --> 10:22.490
This looks really nice.

10:22.980 --> 10:23.840
Come, bride and groom.

10:23.840 --> 10:25.360
Let's move to the front of the car for a photo.

10:25.360 --> 10:25.780
Okay.

10:26.390 --> 10:27.000
Let's go together.

10:27.000 --> 10:28.400
You guys go ahead.

10:29.120 --> 10:30.330
Go, go, go.

10:31.440 --> 10:32.500
Come, groom, stand here.

10:32.500 --> 10:33.630
Bride, stand there.

10:34.220 --> 10:35.550
Does this car look nice?

10:36.030 --> 10:36.980
Hold hands. Hold hands.

10:36.980 --> 10:38.580
Bride and groom, hold hands.

10:42.660 --> 10:44.150
[Suyuan Chun Fresh Corn Juice]

11:27.080 --> 11:31.130
[Cao Ye Qigong Research Center]

11:33.370 --> 11:35.720
[Paris, France]

11:51.010 --> 11:51.940
Tao Liangliang.

11:57.670 --> 11:58.870
I got hired by the travel agency.

11:58.870 --> 12:00.140
I can start work tomorrow.

12:00.140 --> 12:01.080
In a couple of days,

12:01.080 --> 12:02.100
there will be a small Chinese tour group

12:02.100 --> 12:03.050
for me to host.

12:03.480 --> 12:04.940
We'll have an income soon.

12:04.980 --> 12:07.190
I told you you'd be fine.

12:07.570 --> 12:09.300
Shall we go to the supermarket?

12:09.950 --> 12:11.950
You have to introduce to me first

12:11.980 --> 12:12.800
what tourist attractions

12:12.800 --> 12:14.060
there are around here.

12:15.220 --> 12:16.030
This one

12:16.150 --> 12:17.290
is Chaillot Palace.

12:20.150 --> 12:21.990
My hourly rate is very expensive.

12:21.990 --> 12:22.920
Very expensive?

12:23.360 --> 12:24.580
Then tell me,

12:24.740 --> 12:26.360
how can I afford

12:26.360 --> 12:28.050
such an expensive hourly rate?

12:28.050 --> 12:29.560
Make me a nice meal.

12:29.960 --> 12:30.370
Sure.

12:30.390 --> 12:31.160
How nice?

12:31.320 --> 12:34.210
I want to eat Zhajiangmian.

12:34.500 --> 12:35.610
Let's go to the supermarket.

12:35.610 --> 12:36.230
Let's go.

12:37.240 --> 12:38.790
Dear friends,

12:38.820 --> 12:42.000
right in front of you

12:42.030 --> 12:45.550
is the most famous landmark in Paris, France,

12:45.600 --> 12:47.410
the Eiffel Tower.

12:47.790 --> 12:50.670
It was completed in 1889.

12:51.220 --> 12:52.050
Ahead,

12:52.080 --> 12:54.990
the left side is the Museum of Mankind.

12:55.050 --> 12:56.070
On the right,

12:56.100 --> 12:58.860
is the City of Architecture and Heritage.

13:28.230 --> 13:30.980
[Beijing, China]

13:28.370 --> 13:29.720
Come take a look!

13:29.720 --> 13:32.260
All down jackets on clearance sale!

13:32.430 --> 13:33.530
Very cheap!

13:34.460 --> 13:35.960
Brother, look at this jacket.

13:35.960 --> 13:36.940
Buy one for your girlfriend.

13:36.940 --> 13:37.290
Isn't it nice?

13:37.290 --> 13:38.220
Just bought one.

13:38.220 --> 13:39.750
Thank you. Just bought one.

13:40.700 --> 13:41.520
Come again.

13:42.120 --> 13:42.730
Meng.

13:43.360 --> 13:43.790
Mr. Xu.

13:43.790 --> 13:45.290
Why are you doing a clearance sale?

13:45.290 --> 13:47.090
Aren't your goods selling well?

13:49.080 --> 13:50.580
You know how I am.

13:50.670 --> 13:52.320
I don't have my own production line.

13:52.320 --> 13:53.240
I rely on

13:53.240 --> 13:54.500
buying and reselling every day.

13:54.500 --> 13:56.740
One moment the supplier raises the price,

13:56.740 --> 13:58.400
the next, the orders are gone.

13:58.550 --> 14:00.520
Who can stand this?

14:00.960 --> 14:02.210
I borrowed money

14:02.500 --> 14:03.670
to stock up on goods these two months.

14:03.670 --> 14:05.200
Then some bastard showed up

14:05.370 --> 14:07.120
and used a really dirty trick.

14:07.370 --> 14:09.080
He pushed the price of the same goods

14:09.080 --> 14:10.680
down to the absolute lowest.

14:10.890 --> 14:11.670
With the little money I have,

14:11.670 --> 14:12.940
robbing Peter to pay Paul

14:12.940 --> 14:14.200
and tossing it around,

14:14.220 --> 14:15.440
the little profit left in the end

14:15.440 --> 14:16.770
isn't even enough to cover the interest.

14:16.770 --> 14:18.250
The market is bad right now.

14:18.250 --> 14:19.650
It's not easy for anyone.

14:19.960 --> 14:21.350
If you need any help,

14:21.440 --> 14:22.370
just let me know.

14:22.910 --> 14:23.480
Right.

14:23.720 --> 14:26.360
I heard you two negotiated with a factory.

14:26.740 --> 14:27.250
Are you planning

14:27.250 --> 14:29.110
to start production yourselves?

14:29.250 --> 14:31.050
Didn't you just say so yourself?

14:31.320 --> 14:32.890
Relying purely on reselling

14:32.890 --> 14:33.940
is not reliable.

14:34.030 --> 14:35.650
- There are too many unstable factors.
- Yes.

14:35.650 --> 14:36.620
So we figured,

14:36.650 --> 14:37.750
instead of tying our money up in goods,

14:37.750 --> 14:39.940
it's better to find a new way out.

14:41.240 --> 14:42.600
We plan

14:42.720 --> 14:44.480
to create our own brand.

14:45.390 --> 14:46.470
That's great!

14:47.670 --> 14:50.130
Zhuang Zhuang's designs are really pretty.

14:50.530 --> 14:51.360
If you ask me,

14:51.390 --> 14:52.290
you guys should have

14:52.290 --> 14:53.480
started your own brand

14:53.480 --> 14:54.670
a long time ago.

14:54.890 --> 14:57.320
Okay, thanks for the good word.

14:58.340 --> 14:58.770
Brother,

14:58.770 --> 15:00.360
I have another question for you.

15:00.360 --> 15:00.910
Go ahead.

15:02.510 --> 15:03.650
A couple of days ago,

15:03.650 --> 15:05.250
I was walking past your door,

15:05.440 --> 15:06.240
and I saw a hiring sign

15:06.240 --> 15:07.160
on your door.

15:07.530 --> 15:09.730
What kind of person are you looking for?

15:10.390 --> 15:11.120
The thing is,

15:11.530 --> 15:12.220
you and Zhuang Zhuang

15:12.220 --> 15:13.270
are such nice people.

15:13.270 --> 15:14.670
I want to work with you guys.

15:14.670 --> 15:15.600
Perfect timing.

15:15.600 --> 15:17.800
We just got our registered brand,

15:18.240 --> 15:19.200
and we're short on hands.

15:19.200 --> 15:20.000
And here you are.

15:20.000 --> 15:21.080
What a coincidence.

15:21.080 --> 15:21.870
Hurry up and pack your things.

15:21.870 --> 15:23.500
Once you're done, go to my shop.

15:23.500 --> 15:23.820
Okay.

15:23.820 --> 15:25.250
The first batch of goods for our brand

15:25.250 --> 15:25.910
is arriving soon.

15:25.910 --> 15:27.170
I have to go receive it.

15:28.770 --> 15:29.300
Brother.

15:29.790 --> 15:31.120
I heard

15:31.120 --> 15:32.930
there's a line at the garage.

15:33.270 --> 15:34.910
It's been jammed since morning.

15:34.910 --> 15:35.830
That can't be.

15:36.080 --> 15:37.600
I was second in line to get in today.

15:37.600 --> 15:38.480
Ms. Zhang in front of me

15:38.480 --> 15:39.740
doesn't have that much cargo either.

15:39.740 --> 15:41.740
I heard they're not moving goods in.

15:42.200 --> 15:43.290
They were shipping out last night

15:43.290 --> 15:45.020
and haven't finished loading.

15:47.480 --> 15:48.540
Guangfa Commerce.

15:49.340 --> 15:49.980
Yeah.

15:51.480 --> 15:52.510
When Chen Guangfa

15:52.630 --> 15:54.570
ships out, it's a huge batch.

15:54.740 --> 15:56.650
The shipment to Russia this month,

15:56.650 --> 15:58.620
It's all being restocked via charter flights.

15:58.620 --> 16:00.340
There are six or seven tons of clothes.

16:00.340 --> 16:01.630
No matter how much cargo he has,

16:01.630 --> 16:02.340
he can't block

16:02.340 --> 16:04.000
other merchants' access.

16:04.510 --> 16:05.590
I know, right?

16:06.240 --> 16:07.870
But there's nothing we can do.

16:07.870 --> 16:08.980
He is

16:09.030 --> 16:10.960
the Down Jacket King of Yabao Road.

16:11.200 --> 16:12.530
You know his relationship

16:12.530 --> 16:14.170
with Manager Wang, don't you?

16:14.170 --> 16:15.250
Should I go take a look with you?

16:15.250 --> 16:15.710
No need.

16:16.510 --> 16:17.170
You go ahead.

16:17.170 --> 16:18.170
Hurry up and pack.

16:18.220 --> 16:19.020
I'll go check.

16:20.270 --> 16:22.400
Call me if you need anything, brother.

16:27.030 --> 16:28.120
Come take a look.

16:28.150 --> 16:30.660
Down jackets on clearance, very cheap.

16:40.670 --> 16:41.390
Mr. Chen.

16:42.530 --> 16:43.460
Nice to meet you.

16:43.720 --> 16:44.940
Let me introduce myself.

16:44.940 --> 16:45.950
I am Xu Shengli,

16:46.030 --> 16:48.140
and I also have a shop here.

16:56.000 --> 16:56.720
Xu.

17:06.920 --> 17:08.609
Mr. Xu, right?

17:10.220 --> 17:11.220
I've heard of you.

17:11.920 --> 17:13.980
In the Russian commercial district,

17:14.609 --> 17:15.810
you are quite famous.

17:16.230 --> 17:17.440
You flatter me.

17:17.680 --> 17:19.180
You are the real veteran here.

17:19.180 --> 17:20.530
When our shop first opened,

17:20.530 --> 17:21.589
I came to visit you.

17:21.849 --> 17:22.640
You weren't here at the time,

17:22.640 --> 17:23.510
so I just said hello

17:23.510 --> 17:24.369
to the manager.

17:24.640 --> 17:25.700
So I thought

17:25.980 --> 17:27.440
I should come visit again.

17:29.350 --> 17:30.150
Have some tea.

17:30.270 --> 17:33.980
[Guangfa Commerce]

17:51.250 --> 17:52.450
You didn't come today

17:52.940 --> 17:54.400
just to drink tea, did you?

17:54.440 --> 18:03.610
[Guangfa Commerce]

17:56.570 --> 17:58.570
Then I'll get straight to the point.

17:58.830 --> 18:00.360
I just went to the basement.

18:00.570 --> 18:01.800
Our unloading area

18:01.830 --> 18:02.290
is full of

18:02.290 --> 18:03.900
the goods you didn't finish unloading yesterday.

18:03.900 --> 18:05.430
My goods are arriving soon,

18:05.440 --> 18:06.510
and it's a large amount.

18:06.510 --> 18:07.500
If they pile up at the door,

18:07.500 --> 18:08.520
my goods can't get in

18:08.520 --> 18:09.850
and yours can't get out.

18:10.010 --> 18:11.720
Wouldn't that delay your business too?

18:11.720 --> 18:12.270
Then we'll have

18:12.270 --> 18:14.070
nothing to do but drink tea here.

18:15.530 --> 18:16.200
Your business

18:16.200 --> 18:18.460
has been doing well these past few years.

18:19.110 --> 18:19.880
I really appreciate it.

18:19.880 --> 18:22.280
The way young people do business nowadays.

18:22.580 --> 18:23.510
Especially you.

18:24.310 --> 18:25.640
You look like a scholar,

18:25.960 --> 18:28.420
but actually, you have a lot of personality.

18:28.590 --> 18:30.190
You're cut out for business.

18:32.830 --> 18:33.910
There's something

18:34.610 --> 18:35.870
I want to ask you about.

18:37.110 --> 18:37.570
Why

18:37.590 --> 18:39.390
would you switch to down jackets

18:40.960 --> 18:43.690
when your leather shoe business is doing so well?

18:46.480 --> 18:48.250
It's a long story.

18:48.920 --> 18:51.410
If you're really interested,

18:51.920 --> 18:53.550
we can talk about it in detail some other day.

18:53.550 --> 18:55.280
I'm a straightforward person,

18:55.440 --> 18:56.910
so please excuse me, Mr. Chen.

18:56.910 --> 18:58.000
Shouldn't we

18:58.000 --> 19:00.180
solve the problem at hand right now?

19:00.720 --> 19:01.580
What do you say?

19:12.190 --> 19:18.380
[Guangfa Commerce]

19:17.180 --> 19:18.310
Thank you, Mr. Chen.

19:24.420 --> 19:26.280
What time will your goods arrive?

19:26.650 --> 19:28.650
We'll unload by 10:30 at the latest.

19:35.980 --> 19:36.820
Before 10:00,

19:36.940 --> 19:38.400
clear the unloading area.

19:39.500 --> 19:41.400
Thanks for the favor, Mr. Chen.

19:41.440 --> 19:41.850
You're welcome.

19:41.850 --> 19:42.310
Thanks.

19:42.550 --> 19:43.750
Just making a friend.

19:43.880 --> 19:45.140
We definitely should.

19:45.700 --> 19:47.160
I'll get back to work then.

19:48.900 --> 19:49.510
Xu.

19:49.690 --> 19:51.220
[Guangfa Commerce]

19:53.850 --> 19:54.580
Every place

19:54.920 --> 19:56.010
has its own rules.

19:57.440 --> 19:58.030
Every industry

19:58.030 --> 19:59.150
has its own tricks.

19:59.850 --> 20:00.680
Just because

20:00.680 --> 20:02.200
the down jacket business has been booming recently,

20:02.200 --> 20:04.050
doesn't mean you should force your way in.

20:04.050 --> 20:06.740
It's really hard to make it work.

20:08.500 --> 20:09.700
If I had your leather shoe business,

20:09.700 --> 20:11.690
which is so stable.

20:13.530 --> 20:14.590
I wouldn't do anything

20:14.590 --> 20:16.650
that touches someone else's cheese.

20:17.250 --> 20:18.850
Mr. Chen, you must be joking.

20:18.980 --> 20:20.570
In this world,

20:20.830 --> 20:21.960
no business is easy.

20:22.240 --> 20:22.920
When we were

20:22.940 --> 20:23.980
in the leather shoe business,

20:23.980 --> 20:25.700
we also struggled all the way.

20:26.290 --> 20:27.690
Whether it's easy or not,

20:27.980 --> 20:29.720
you have to do it to know.

20:30.140 --> 20:31.400
Mr. Chen, don't worry.

20:32.000 --> 20:34.260
I'm ready to pay my dues.

20:34.980 --> 20:36.780
You are considered

20:37.610 --> 20:38.670
a big brother here.

20:38.770 --> 20:40.810
So please look after me from now on.

20:41.160 --> 20:42.090
I'll get to work.

20:50.580 --> 20:59.810
[Beijing MRX Trading Co., Ltd.]

20:53.010 --> 20:53.580
Honey,

20:53.810 --> 20:54.350
come down quickly.

20:54.350 --> 20:55.010
Let me do it.

20:55.440 --> 20:56.100
Let me do it.

20:56.220 --> 20:57.480
Okay, I'm done wiping.

21:05.980 --> 21:07.170
MRX.

21:07.590 --> 21:09.190
It sounds warm,

21:09.350 --> 21:10.550
and has brand warmth.

21:11.700 --> 21:12.900
And our logo

21:13.500 --> 21:14.630
is designed so well.

21:15.290 --> 21:16.000
We actually

21:16.000 --> 21:17.640
have our own brand.

21:19.920 --> 21:20.660
This is the first step

21:20.660 --> 21:21.930
of our dream.

21:22.590 --> 21:23.380
Then next,

21:23.610 --> 21:25.480
our MRX will...

21:25.830 --> 21:26.890
Selling to Russia,

21:27.010 --> 21:27.960
to Eastern Europe,

21:27.960 --> 21:29.300
and to North America.

21:29.590 --> 21:30.670
By then,

21:30.740 --> 21:31.900
we won't just

21:31.900 --> 21:32.960
have down jackets.

21:33.070 --> 21:34.280
What we'll do is

21:34.420 --> 21:36.890
the MRX brand series.

21:37.050 --> 21:39.500
Menswear, womenswear, kidswear,

21:40.590 --> 21:41.720
and custom dresses.

21:42.010 --> 21:43.570
Dresses are called MRX too?

21:43.720 --> 21:44.800
Absolutely.

21:45.400 --> 21:46.380
My wife came up with it.

21:46.380 --> 21:47.330
It's such a nice name,

21:47.330 --> 21:48.660
we have to keep using it.

21:51.440 --> 21:52.050
Let's

21:52.050 --> 21:53.000
first establish a foothold

21:53.000 --> 21:54.120
here on Yabao Road.

21:54.480 --> 21:55.530
Look at how many people

21:55.530 --> 21:57.790
are selling down jackets in this market.

21:58.090 --> 21:59.580
The market is good,

21:59.700 --> 22:00.720
but for people like us

22:00.720 --> 22:02.060
who barge in blindly,

22:02.160 --> 22:03.250
we still need to be careful

22:03.250 --> 22:04.850
and take it one step at a time.

22:06.290 --> 22:07.090
What's wrong?

22:07.720 --> 22:09.550
Someone just said

22:09.630 --> 22:11.350
something similar to what you did.

22:11.350 --> 22:12.010
Who?

22:13.750 --> 22:15.280
The down jacket king

22:15.380 --> 22:16.630
around here.

22:17.030 --> 22:17.790
Mr. Chen?

22:18.510 --> 22:20.510
How did you two bump into each other?

22:20.940 --> 22:22.330
Thanks to this king,

22:22.330 --> 22:23.030
our goods arrived

22:23.030 --> 22:25.230
on time today.

22:26.570 --> 22:28.220
He said the same thing as me?

22:28.660 --> 22:29.650
Pretty much.

22:30.250 --> 22:31.330
Actually, I always feel

22:31.330 --> 22:31.900
that he seems

22:31.900 --> 22:34.400
a bit hostile towards us.

22:35.500 --> 22:35.900
Him?

22:35.900 --> 22:36.550
Come on.

22:37.070 --> 22:37.670
It's here.

22:38.640 --> 22:39.660
Hello. Who is Mr. Xu?

22:39.660 --> 22:40.270
Hello, I am.

22:40.270 --> 22:40.790
Hello.

22:40.830 --> 22:41.700
Um, your goods have arrived.

22:41.700 --> 22:42.330
Come on.

22:42.530 --> 22:43.200
Put it inside.

22:43.200 --> 22:44.090
Okay, okay.

22:44.090 --> 22:45.480
Hurry and unload it. Come on.

22:45.480 --> 22:46.910
Come on, put it inside.

22:47.270 --> 22:48.990
Ten boxes. Okay.

22:50.290 --> 22:50.790
Okay.

22:50.790 --> 22:52.030
It's okay. We'll do it ourselves.

22:52.030 --> 22:52.530
Okay.

22:54.010 --> 22:54.860
Thanks for your hard work.

22:54.860 --> 22:56.000
- Here you are.
- It’s OK.

22:56.000 --> 22:56.440
Okay.

22:56.500 --> 22:56.880
Thank you.

22:56.880 --> 22:57.530
- Thank you.
- If everything is here...

22:57.530 --> 22:58.990
- Yes, yes, yes.
- We’ll leave if there’s nothing else.

22:58.990 --> 22:59.690
Okay.

23:00.050 --> 23:00.550
I'll let you get on.

23:00.550 --> 23:01.110
Okay.

23:01.420 --> 23:02.420
Let's go. Come on.

23:08.480 --> 23:09.210
I'll do it.

23:17.400 --> 23:18.260
So good.

23:18.400 --> 23:19.030
These bulk goods

23:19.030 --> 23:21.160
are made even better than the samples.

23:21.420 --> 23:23.550
I'll put them on the models right away.

23:24.740 --> 23:26.570
Now I know why Mr. Chen

23:26.570 --> 23:28.090
is so hostile towards us.

23:29.050 --> 23:30.780
With our quality being so good,

23:30.980 --> 23:31.700
he's worried that

23:31.700 --> 23:33.860
we'll steal his crown.

23:33.980 --> 23:35.080
Look at you.

23:35.880 --> 23:37.480
No wonder he singled you out.

23:37.610 --> 23:38.960
Let him.

23:38.960 --> 23:40.640
I just tell the truth.

23:45.980 --> 23:46.910
Secretary Sang,

23:47.590 --> 23:48.940
is this Chairman Luo

23:49.030 --> 23:49.880
the same one

23:49.880 --> 23:51.280
Mr. Lu mentioned before,

23:51.510 --> 23:53.380
the legend in the investment world?

23:53.380 --> 23:53.790
Yes.

23:54.570 --> 23:55.570
It's not convenient for the chairman

23:55.570 --> 23:57.030
to show up in public often.

23:57.330 --> 23:58.250
Calling you to his home

23:58.250 --> 23:59.510
to help him recuperate

23:59.680 --> 24:00.940
shows his trust in you.

24:01.330 --> 24:01.950
When you're out,

24:01.950 --> 24:03.480
you must keep a low profile.

24:03.590 --> 24:04.010
Okay.

24:05.740 --> 24:06.340
By the way,

24:06.660 --> 24:08.360
I must reiterate,

24:08.940 --> 24:10.320
You must not tell anyone

24:10.700 --> 24:12.080
about today's visit.

24:12.570 --> 24:13.740
You can't breathe a word

24:13.740 --> 24:15.460
about what you see and hear either.

24:15.460 --> 24:16.390
Behave yourself

24:16.530 --> 24:17.940
when you see the Chairman.

24:17.940 --> 24:19.550
If the Chairman doesn't offer a handshake,

24:19.550 --> 24:21.480
you shouldn't reach out your hand.

24:36.110 --> 24:36.880
Chairman.

24:38.790 --> 24:39.920
Impure qi is rising.

24:39.960 --> 24:41.420
It's better to spit it out.

24:46.770 --> 24:48.570
I've been coughing a lot lately.

24:49.290 --> 24:50.620
I took a lot of medicine,

24:50.980 --> 24:52.810
and hired many doctors,

24:54.660 --> 24:57.380
but there's still no improvement.

24:57.720 --> 25:00.180
Because this cough is not an ordinary cough.

25:01.740 --> 25:03.030
What's the difference?

25:03.030 --> 25:04.230
In 1994,

25:04.250 --> 25:05.980
a Japanese research institute

25:06.240 --> 25:06.810
started

25:06.810 --> 25:08.340
a study on water molecules.

25:09.680 --> 25:10.680
Water molecules?

25:11.750 --> 25:13.150
I'll make it short.

25:13.270 --> 25:14.220
It means

25:14.440 --> 25:15.700
pouring the same water

25:15.850 --> 25:17.450
into different containers.

25:17.960 --> 25:19.030
One container is labeled

25:19.030 --> 25:20.380
with beautiful blessings,

25:20.380 --> 25:21.380
and the other side

25:21.440 --> 25:23.240
is labeled with vicious curses.

25:23.700 --> 25:25.070
Both put into the freezer at the same time.

25:25.070 --> 25:26.720
After the water becomes ice crystals,

25:26.720 --> 25:28.240
observing them under a microscope,

25:28.240 --> 25:30.940
they found their forms are completely different.

25:30.940 --> 25:31.640
So,

25:31.770 --> 25:34.030
because of an encounter in my childhood,

25:34.030 --> 25:35.400
I can inject my thoughts

25:35.400 --> 25:36.700
into your body

25:36.900 --> 25:38.440
to communicate

25:38.440 --> 25:39.400
with the water molecules in your body,

25:39.400 --> 25:40.860
making them stronger.

25:41.140 --> 25:43.400
You will naturally get well and recover.

25:47.160 --> 25:48.690
Sounds quite interesting.

25:56.840 --> 25:58.240
Did you have fun, my baby?

26:00.920 --> 26:02.180
I don't want to go home.

26:04.330 --> 26:06.100
Seems like you're tired from playing.

26:06.100 --> 26:07.160
I have a guest here.

26:07.770 --> 26:08.770
You go rest first.

26:15.890 --> 26:17.770
Let's continue.

26:18.180 --> 26:18.550
Okay.

26:24.980 --> 26:26.700
Thank you for your hard work, Master Cao.

26:26.700 --> 26:27.890
It's my duty.

26:28.420 --> 26:29.720
The chairman's illness

26:29.720 --> 26:31.150
is caused by overwork

26:31.240 --> 26:33.400
and the accumulation of stagnant qi in his body.

26:33.400 --> 26:34.320
It's not mild,

26:34.420 --> 26:35.350
but don't worry.

26:35.570 --> 26:37.670
As long as I use my mind

26:37.880 --> 26:39.200
to transform the water molecules in his body

26:39.200 --> 26:40.190
a few more times,

26:40.440 --> 26:41.770
he will surely recover.

26:43.610 --> 26:44.990
Thank you, Master Cao.

26:45.090 --> 26:46.090
Thank you so much.

26:46.610 --> 26:47.690
You're welcome.

26:47.850 --> 26:49.350
It's because of your trust.

26:49.350 --> 26:50.660
The chairman also gave me an opportunity.

26:50.660 --> 26:52.120
I must thank you very much.

26:53.220 --> 26:53.980
Master Cao.

26:54.240 --> 26:56.330
I suppose you have heard Mr. Lu mention this before.

26:56.330 --> 26:57.280
Our chairman

26:57.380 --> 26:58.880
has a unique eye for investment.

26:58.880 --> 27:01.550
All the projects he invests in are highly profitable.

27:01.550 --> 27:02.450
I hope

27:02.640 --> 27:03.350
I will have the chance in the future

27:03.350 --> 27:04.670
to be guided by him.

27:05.270 --> 27:05.890
By the way,

27:06.530 --> 27:08.570
who is that ''baby''?

27:09.030 --> 27:10.830
She is the chairman's daughter.

27:11.530 --> 27:13.010
Look at these

27:13.160 --> 27:14.260
in the corridor,

27:14.400 --> 27:16.400
They were all collected by Miss Luo.

27:21.680 --> 27:23.210
So this Miss Luo

27:23.790 --> 27:25.590
truly has extraordinary taste.

27:27.110 --> 27:28.050
Perhaps because of this

27:28.050 --> 27:29.310
extraordinary taste,

27:29.590 --> 27:30.920
she hasn't met

27:30.940 --> 27:31.940
her Mr. Right yet.

27:35.380 --> 27:37.950
Master Cao, you are also a young talent.

27:38.770 --> 27:40.180
Are you married?

27:46.590 --> 27:48.110
Don't worry, honey.

27:48.180 --> 27:50.090
I've checked the quality of our goods.

27:50.090 --> 27:51.220
Everything is fine.

27:51.510 --> 27:52.050
Okay.

27:52.750 --> 27:54.150
Shengli, Zhuangzhuang.

27:54.500 --> 27:56.090
The garage has been registered.

27:56.090 --> 27:57.180
When customers come to pick up the goods,

27:57.180 --> 27:58.590
we can just move them down.

27:58.590 --> 27:59.310
Thank you.

27:59.330 --> 28:00.590
You really know your stuff.

28:00.590 --> 28:01.250
Not at all.

28:04.090 --> 28:04.740
Mr. Xu.

28:05.030 --> 28:06.120
Mr. Anton.

28:06.270 --> 28:06.920
Welcome.

28:06.960 --> 28:07.900
Welcome.

28:07.900 --> 28:10.050
- Have a seat.
- Come on. Have a seat. Get some water.

28:10.050 --> 28:11.350
We have prepared all the goods.

28:11.350 --> 28:12.480
Let's inspect them.

28:14.270 --> 28:14.920
No need to inspect.

28:14.920 --> 28:16.210
I have seen them many times.

28:16.210 --> 28:17.450
You did very well.

28:17.850 --> 28:19.850
Thank you for your trust, Mr. Anton.

28:20.110 --> 28:21.790
How long will the relabeling take?

28:21.790 --> 28:23.270
I'll pick them up in a week.

28:27.420 --> 28:27.980
Relabeling?

28:27.980 --> 28:30.790
You mean changing the origin labels?

28:32.090 --> 28:34.270
You've been in this business for so long,

28:34.270 --> 28:36.480
don't you know our rules?

28:37.790 --> 28:39.520
Mr. Anton, please don't worry.

28:39.570 --> 28:41.170
It's just replacing labels.

28:41.330 --> 28:42.380
We can rework quickly.

28:42.380 --> 28:44.110
- It'll be done in a week.
- Meng,

28:44.400 --> 28:45.200
we won't do it.

28:47.380 --> 28:49.050
When you pass the quality inspection,

28:49.050 --> 28:51.050
you can put on the original country label.

28:51.050 --> 28:52.320
But in Russia,

28:52.480 --> 28:54.210
Chinese goods don't sell well.

28:54.240 --> 28:55.270
Just put on a label saying

28:55.270 --> 28:56.350
made in Italy,

28:56.350 --> 28:57.690
America, wherever.

28:57.940 --> 28:59.220
If you think it's too much trouble,

28:59.220 --> 29:01.150
I can pay a little extra.

29:01.570 --> 29:02.470
Mr. Anton,

29:03.000 --> 29:04.420
it's not about money.

29:05.530 --> 29:07.140
Your request

29:07.140 --> 29:09.220
violates export regulations.

29:09.720 --> 29:10.790
If something happens,

29:10.790 --> 29:12.720
we can't bear the responsibility.

29:16.210 --> 29:16.740
Fine.

29:17.530 --> 29:18.390
Just this once.

29:19.250 --> 29:21.200
Doing business with people like you

29:21.200 --> 29:22.060
is so tiring.

29:22.480 --> 29:23.940
Get the goods ready.

29:24.270 --> 29:26.400
I'll find a place to label them myself.

29:30.090 --> 29:31.360
I'm sorry, Mr. Anton.

29:31.500 --> 29:33.360
Our store doesn't sell OEM goods.

29:34.010 --> 29:35.770
We're not selling these 600 pieces.

29:35.770 --> 29:37.380
The MRXs are made in China.

29:39.140 --> 29:39.860
Mr. Anton,

29:40.000 --> 29:42.210
this is the deposit you paid earlier.

29:42.270 --> 29:43.530
We haven't touched it.

29:43.660 --> 29:44.590
You can check it.

29:54.140 --> 29:54.980
Take care.

30:05.090 --> 30:06.490
Shengli, Zhuangzhuang.

30:08.000 --> 30:09.200
Don't be mad.

30:09.290 --> 30:10.750
Actually, shipping goods to Russia,

30:10.750 --> 30:11.880
there really is such an

30:11.880 --> 30:12.810
unwritten rule.

30:13.250 --> 30:14.310
There are also many

30:14.400 --> 30:15.640
factories specializing in foreign trade

30:15.640 --> 30:17.010
that sew their origin labels on

30:17.010 --> 30:18.270
very loosely.

30:18.610 --> 30:19.420
Some even use glue

30:19.420 --> 30:20.550
to stick them directly.

30:20.550 --> 30:21.290
Once they pass the inspection,

30:21.290 --> 30:22.850
they can be blown off with a hair dryer.

30:22.850 --> 30:24.640
Then no one will know they're made in China.

30:24.640 --> 30:26.000
People buying clothes don't care about this either.

30:26.000 --> 30:27.860
Our job is making money, isn't it?

30:27.960 --> 30:29.020
We care about that.

30:33.940 --> 30:34.960
Have a seat, Meng.

30:37.310 --> 30:38.000
Before this,

30:38.000 --> 30:39.610
when we were selling leather shoes in Russia,

30:39.610 --> 30:41.670
we encountered a similar situation.

30:41.750 --> 30:43.420
They put European and American labels

30:43.420 --> 30:45.920
on high-quality goods and sold them at high prices.

30:45.920 --> 30:47.220
And they put Chinese labels

30:47.220 --> 30:49.220
on defective goods and sold them at low prices.

30:49.220 --> 30:50.530
If this keeps going on,

30:50.940 --> 30:52.940
wouldn't it become a vicious cycle?

30:53.460 --> 30:54.310
In the eyes of foreigners,

30:54.310 --> 30:55.120
Chinese goods

30:55.270 --> 30:58.130
would become synonymous with defective products.

30:58.660 --> 31:00.010
Since we've already decided

31:00.010 --> 31:01.380
to produce them ourselves,

31:01.380 --> 31:02.240
Zhuang and I

31:03.110 --> 31:03.660
still hope

31:03.660 --> 31:05.390
to bring good Chinese products

31:05.740 --> 31:06.610
to the world.

31:12.700 --> 31:14.480
I understand, Shengli.

31:16.000 --> 31:17.220
It's my first day here,

31:17.220 --> 31:18.330
so please don't blame me.

31:18.330 --> 31:19.020
But seeing that you two

31:19.020 --> 31:20.620
are so confident about this,

31:20.720 --> 31:22.010
as long as you have confidence,

31:22.010 --> 31:23.090
so do I.

31:27.750 --> 31:29.860
Honey, let's forget it.

31:30.330 --> 31:31.290
It's only 600 pieces.

31:31.290 --> 31:32.610
I'll sell them all tomorrow.

31:32.610 --> 31:34.120
Right, and you have me.

31:34.250 --> 31:34.790
Right.

31:35.140 --> 31:36.870
The most important thing today

31:37.070 --> 31:37.960
is that Meng

31:38.240 --> 31:40.580
officially joined our MRX.

31:40.720 --> 31:41.310
It is worth celebrating.

31:41.310 --> 31:42.380
Let's replace wine

31:43.050 --> 31:44.290
with water and propose a toast.

31:44.290 --> 31:44.720
Cheers.

31:44.720 --> 31:45.880
All right? Come on.

31:48.940 --> 31:50.620
Then let's wish ourselves

31:51.010 --> 31:53.620
even greater success.

31:53.740 --> 31:55.000
Even greater success.

31:59.960 --> 32:00.830
Mr. Jia, look,

32:00.860 --> 32:01.820
our down jackets

32:01.900 --> 32:02.760
have 90% down,

32:02.830 --> 32:04.030
pure white duck down.

32:04.180 --> 32:05.110
You can touch it.

32:05.110 --> 32:06.120
Feel the texture,

32:06.250 --> 32:07.380
and the resilience.

32:07.510 --> 32:08.470
I can guarantee

32:08.720 --> 32:09.920
that our down jackets

32:09.920 --> 32:11.650
will definitely not leak down.

32:12.610 --> 32:15.270
We've been selling down jackets for ten years.

32:16.010 --> 32:18.010
We can tell good quality at a glance.

32:19.740 --> 32:20.480
But,

32:21.550 --> 32:23.720
you know how the market is right now.

32:24.380 --> 32:26.830
You young people come out to make a living,

32:27.240 --> 32:28.840
and you have determination.

32:29.160 --> 32:29.650
But,

32:30.200 --> 32:31.740
don't blame us old geezers

32:31.740 --> 32:33.140
for being cold-blooded.

32:34.240 --> 32:35.680
We have to support our family.

32:35.680 --> 32:36.920
If I buy stock from you,

32:36.920 --> 32:37.750
and it doesn't sell,

32:37.750 --> 32:39.480
I won't be able to answer for it.

32:40.460 --> 32:41.920
I completely understand.

32:42.070 --> 32:43.040
How about this?

32:43.610 --> 32:45.270
I brought some samples today.

32:45.380 --> 32:47.250
I'll give them all to you

32:47.440 --> 32:48.220
for free.

32:48.700 --> 32:49.420
If they sell well,

32:49.420 --> 32:50.380
you can come back to me,

32:50.380 --> 32:52.420
and I'll give you the lowest price possible.

32:52.420 --> 32:52.900
Mr. Jia,

32:53.590 --> 32:54.680
I am very confident

32:54.830 --> 32:55.880
in our products.

32:59.720 --> 33:01.190
Then let's do this.

33:01.330 --> 33:03.130
Bring me another twenty pieces.

33:03.270 --> 33:04.370
I'll pay for them.

33:04.640 --> 33:05.070
And,

33:05.380 --> 33:06.200
since

33:06.270 --> 33:07.900
I know many distributors,

33:08.180 --> 33:09.910
I'll give them some samples too

33:10.180 --> 33:11.840
to help you open up the market.

33:12.200 --> 33:12.850
Then, Mr. Jia,

33:12.850 --> 33:14.700
about what we discussed before,

33:17.220 --> 33:17.940
no rebranding?

33:17.940 --> 33:18.690
Yes.

33:19.640 --> 33:20.220
About this,

33:20.220 --> 33:22.110
I'll definitely make it clear to them before.

33:22.110 --> 33:24.140
If they can accept it, we'll talk.

33:25.900 --> 33:26.500
Okay.

33:26.680 --> 33:27.720
Thank you, Mr. Jia.

33:27.720 --> 33:29.200
I'll go get the samples for you.

33:29.200 --> 33:30.310
Yes, hurry up.

33:30.380 --> 33:31.530
- Wait a moment.
- Do you need someone to carry it?

33:31.530 --> 33:32.990
No need, I can do it myself.

33:47.770 --> 33:48.850
Dinner time.

34:16.480 --> 34:17.420
Get up and eat.

34:20.260 --> 34:21.520
You must be exhausted.

34:24.070 --> 34:24.600
I'm fine.

34:25.340 --> 34:25.940
Let's eat.

34:28.520 --> 34:30.980
This food looks delicious.

34:33.969 --> 34:35.120
I'm really hungry.

34:37.210 --> 34:38.070
Eat slowly.

34:38.210 --> 34:39.139
It's delicious.

34:39.260 --> 34:40.940
But compared to you,

34:40.960 --> 34:42.090
it's not even close.

34:42.510 --> 34:44.370
I'll cook for you when we get back.

34:46.300 --> 34:47.590
Aren't you curious

34:47.590 --> 34:49.080
how our goods sold today?

34:49.380 --> 34:50.940
Let's finish eating first.

34:55.380 --> 34:56.179
Where is Meng?

34:56.870 --> 34:58.070
I let him go home.

34:58.370 --> 35:00.230
He's been running around all day.

35:01.590 --> 35:02.000
Yeah.

35:04.240 --> 35:05.650
Meng is quite hardworking.

35:05.650 --> 35:06.820
And he's very dedicated

35:06.820 --> 35:07.550
to our shop.

35:09.010 --> 35:10.030
He closed his own shop,

35:10.030 --> 35:11.340
but he didn't lose heart.

35:11.340 --> 35:13.100
He's still very driven.

35:14.340 --> 35:15.230
How about this?

35:17.230 --> 35:18.480
We can take his previous goods

35:18.480 --> 35:19.780
that he wants to clear out,

35:19.780 --> 35:20.610
sell them here,

35:20.610 --> 35:22.110
and give him all the money.

35:22.300 --> 35:23.050
Sure.

35:24.550 --> 35:25.610
He probably bought those goods

35:25.610 --> 35:27.090
with his own savings.

35:27.400 --> 35:28.900
It must be painful for him to be stuck with all this stock.

35:28.900 --> 35:29.780
Let's do it.

35:31.090 --> 35:31.610
Mr. Xu.

35:33.070 --> 35:33.670
Mr. Chen.

35:34.260 --> 35:35.280
You're still in the market so late?

35:35.280 --> 35:35.860
Yeah.

35:36.000 --> 35:37.000
Mr. Chen.

35:37.030 --> 35:37.670
Hello.

35:37.670 --> 35:38.150
Hello.

35:38.230 --> 35:39.420
I've heard so much about you.

35:39.420 --> 35:40.110
Come, sit.

35:40.110 --> 35:41.970
- Okay. - Let me get you some water.

35:42.590 --> 35:43.300
Having a meal?

35:43.300 --> 35:44.570
How about I get you some chopsticks

35:44.570 --> 35:45.260
so you can have a taste?

35:45.260 --> 35:46.390
I've already eaten.

35:46.780 --> 35:47.170
Here.

35:47.630 --> 35:48.420
Okay. Thank you.

35:48.420 --> 35:49.480
Let's talk while you eat.

35:49.480 --> 35:50.230
It's fine.

35:51.060 --> 35:53.390
All right. I'll get straight to the point.

35:55.690 --> 35:56.760
I mentioned this last time.

35:56.760 --> 35:58.690
The down jacket business is tough.

35:58.960 --> 35:59.690
My words might be harsh,

35:59.690 --> 36:00.750
please don't mind.

36:00.900 --> 36:01.500
It's okay.

36:01.610 --> 36:02.410
So I came today

36:02.500 --> 36:04.210
to help you.

36:05.030 --> 36:05.590
Go ahead.

36:07.010 --> 36:08.810
We all do business on Yabao Road.

36:08.920 --> 36:10.320
Friction is inevitable.

36:10.570 --> 36:12.030
But our general direction

36:12.170 --> 36:13.010
is the same.

36:13.550 --> 36:15.510
Only when the whole industry thrives,

36:15.510 --> 36:17.160
can we thrive. Right?

36:17.570 --> 36:18.000
Yes.

36:18.420 --> 36:18.860
Right.

36:19.380 --> 36:21.030
So, I want to

36:21.400 --> 36:24.000
give you some advice as an experienced person.

36:25.550 --> 36:25.980
I know

36:26.000 --> 36:27.910
you look down on OEM products.

36:28.920 --> 36:29.530
But I'm sorry to tell you,

36:29.530 --> 36:31.130
this is what the market needs.

36:31.130 --> 36:33.150
A little compromise

36:33.480 --> 36:35.810
could keep several major plants running.

36:35.840 --> 36:36.860
Just to prove a point,

36:36.860 --> 36:38.460
running a business at a loss,

36:38.860 --> 36:39.940
going hungry yourself,

36:39.940 --> 36:41.540
and letting your men suffer.

36:42.610 --> 36:44.610
That’s just not being responsible.

36:46.130 --> 36:46.780
So,

36:47.300 --> 36:48.840
I can give you

36:48.840 --> 36:50.010
a little support.

36:51.760 --> 36:53.150
I've seen your products.

36:53.150 --> 36:54.610
The quality is excellent.

36:54.820 --> 36:56.180
If they were in my hands,

36:56.400 --> 36:57.280
I could easily pass them off

36:57.280 --> 36:58.840
as European or American goods,

36:58.840 --> 37:00.840
and sell them for the highest price.

37:01.130 --> 37:01.710
So,

37:02.000 --> 37:02.930
I hope from now on

37:03.030 --> 37:04.900
you can process them for me.

37:05.030 --> 37:06.210
You handle production,

37:06.210 --> 37:07.610
and I handle sales.

37:08.480 --> 37:09.030
Also, I have

37:09.030 --> 37:10.510
what you need the most.

37:11.780 --> 37:12.280
Money.

37:12.960 --> 37:14.940
I can provide the upfront capital for you,

37:14.940 --> 37:17.110
so you can at least get food on the table.

37:17.110 --> 37:19.040
But it’s not just about getting by,

37:19.210 --> 37:20.540
it’s about living well.

37:20.980 --> 37:22.110
How does that sound?

37:22.650 --> 37:24.030
Here's the thing, Mr. Chen.

37:24.030 --> 37:24.690
It's not that we

37:24.690 --> 37:26.150
look down on OEM products.

37:26.170 --> 37:27.940
We just don't want to sell OEM products.

37:27.940 --> 37:29.340
- It must be...
- Mr. Chen.

37:31.110 --> 37:32.640
Our business philosophies

37:33.380 --> 37:34.380
are fundamentally different.

37:34.380 --> 37:35.870
There’s no common ground.

37:36.280 --> 37:38.360
Let’s pass on this partnership.

37:54.190 --> 37:54.920
Sorry to bother you.

37:54.920 --> 37:55.680
Take care.

37:56.780 --> 37:58.710
Look at him. It's quite cute.

37:59.320 --> 38:00.850
What kind of person is that?

38:01.570 --> 38:02.530
Doing the wrong thing himself

38:02.530 --> 38:03.720
and wanting to drag us into it.

38:03.720 --> 38:05.090
Honey, don't be angry.

38:05.460 --> 38:06.860
Don't stoop to his level.

38:07.630 --> 38:08.510
At least he said

38:08.530 --> 38:09.770
our bear is cute.

38:10.280 --> 38:11.360
Just eat.

38:26.510 --> 38:28.170
Mr. Chen, you wanted to see me?

38:30.210 --> 38:31.520
Got a new job,

38:31.940 --> 38:33.600
so you ignore your old friend?

38:34.110 --> 38:36.170
Mr. Chen, what are you talking about?

38:36.940 --> 38:38.340
How are things over there?

38:38.340 --> 38:39.070
Pretty good.

38:42.130 --> 38:43.730
That couple is too stubborn.

38:45.000 --> 38:45.590
Don't you agree

38:45.590 --> 38:47.050
that this won't work out?

38:50.800 --> 38:52.050
Mr. Xu and Zhuang

38:52.460 --> 38:53.760
just lack experience.

38:54.170 --> 38:55.500
They've had it too easy.

38:55.730 --> 38:57.050
Maybe if they hit the wall sometime,

38:57.050 --> 38:57.910
they'll learn.

38:58.170 --> 38:58.940
You've been in this market

38:58.940 --> 39:00.030
for so many years.

39:01.280 --> 39:03.740
Have you ever seen anyone succeed like this?

39:04.230 --> 39:05.360
How long can you last

39:06.190 --> 39:07.450
on that meager salary?

39:08.170 --> 39:09.780
Your own business went belly up,

39:09.780 --> 39:11.380
and you’re drowning in debt.

39:11.400 --> 39:13.130
If you want to stay in the shade,

39:14.690 --> 39:16.650
you’d better find yourself a big tree.

39:16.650 --> 39:17.500
Mr. Chen,

39:17.900 --> 39:19.450
I really had no choice.

39:19.590 --> 39:20.650
Why not?

39:24.860 --> 39:25.720
You need money.

39:27.880 --> 39:29.280
You could have come to me.

39:29.710 --> 39:31.380
You know they're against me.

39:32.090 --> 39:33.350
Instead of helping me,

39:34.610 --> 39:36.410
you joined them to screw me over.

39:37.050 --> 39:37.580
Mr. Chen,

39:39.010 --> 39:40.710
who dares to go against you?

39:40.900 --> 39:41.630
Doesn't the whole market

39:41.630 --> 39:43.230
just pick up your leftovers?

39:43.480 --> 39:44.810
Cut the crap.

39:45.090 --> 39:45.750
Right here.

39:47.380 --> 39:48.640
Partnering with them,

39:49.780 --> 39:51.310
means standing against me.

39:52.110 --> 39:53.240
To be my enemy,

39:53.630 --> 39:55.160
you've heard what happens,

39:57.010 --> 39:57.900
right?

39:59.190 --> 40:01.370
Mr. Chen, what are you getting at?

40:02.110 --> 40:03.110
This young couple

40:04.460 --> 40:05.390
broke the rules.

40:05.840 --> 40:07.500
But I didn't make these rules,

40:08.630 --> 40:10.110
Yabao Road did.

40:11.500 --> 40:13.560
The entire foreign trade market did.

40:13.880 --> 40:15.680
I’m just representing our peers

40:15.880 --> 40:17.740
to protect our common interests.

40:17.980 --> 40:18.550
Right?

40:21.260 --> 40:21.860
So,

40:22.980 --> 40:24.380
I hope you stick with them

40:25.210 --> 40:26.010
and work hard.

40:27.270 --> 40:29.270
- Mr. Chen, don’t...
- Let me finish.

40:29.630 --> 40:30.800
Work hard with them

40:32.150 --> 40:33.280
and win their trust.

40:34.320 --> 40:35.720
I'll find an opportunity

40:36.030 --> 40:36.890
to devour them.

40:37.490 --> 40:40.230
Bears, wolves, whatever,

40:40.940 --> 40:42.050
they'll all be yours.

40:42.050 --> 40:42.630
Mine?

40:42.650 --> 40:43.150
Yours.

40:59.420 --> 41:00.190
Mr. Chen.

41:01.530 --> 41:02.090
So,

41:02.460 --> 41:04.000
how long will this take?

41:04.750 --> 41:05.400
Mr. Xu,

41:05.670 --> 41:07.060
That Xu Shengli...

41:07.190 --> 41:08.860
He’s actually a very meticulous man.

41:08.860 --> 41:10.480
I'm afraid I'll be exposed if it takes too long.

41:10.480 --> 41:11.810
Don't be in such a hurry.

41:13.550 --> 41:15.940
Have you ever seen someone harvesting apples?

41:15.940 --> 41:17.200
When the fruit is ripe,

41:17.510 --> 41:19.230
one single strike with the pole,

41:19.230 --> 41:20.760
saves both time and effort.

41:21.000 --> 41:22.400
Don't ask any questions.

41:23.110 --> 41:24.510
Just remember one thing,

41:25.340 --> 41:26.740
Stick with me to get rich,

41:28.030 --> 41:29.830
and you will prosper all the way.

41:40.930 --> 41:42.770
The chairman only told me half of it.

41:42.770 --> 41:44.330
Is he unwilling to help me?

41:44.710 --> 41:45.840
Master Cao.

41:46.150 --> 41:46.880
There are many things

41:46.880 --> 41:48.360
that you still haven't figured out.

41:48.360 --> 41:49.110
Well,

41:49.130 --> 41:50.860
I have you to back me up, don't I?

41:50.860 --> 41:52.600
Why don't you just tell me directly

41:52.600 --> 41:54.250
what I should do?

41:54.400 --> 41:55.320
The chairman promised

41:55.320 --> 41:56.640
to do you a small favor.

41:56.840 --> 41:57.800
And right away you expect him

41:57.800 --> 41:59.200
to guide your every move?

41:59.210 --> 42:00.550
Didn't I tell you?

42:00.570 --> 42:01.530
The chairman's guidance

42:01.530 --> 42:02.960
needs to be won at an auction.

42:02.960 --> 42:05.160
Do you know how much that auction costs?

42:05.900 --> 42:07.430
What the chairman told you,

42:07.510 --> 42:09.110
have you completely forgotten?

42:09.110 --> 42:10.250
Investments.

42:10.480 --> 42:11.970
It's about high stakes.

42:12.510 --> 42:13.340
No matter how small,

42:13.340 --> 42:14.790
you must invest first

42:14.820 --> 42:15.710
to get a return.

42:17.260 --> 42:17.880
Right.

42:18.360 --> 42:19.380
So now,

42:19.460 --> 42:20.840
in which direction

42:20.900 --> 42:22.160
should I invest first?

42:23.440 --> 42:24.350
About this,

42:24.400 --> 42:25.930
I dare not help you anymore.

42:28.030 --> 42:29.160
Put this over there.

42:42.900 --> 42:44.760
Are you interested in paintings?

42:52.670 --> 42:54.020
Where did this painting come from?
